text: Eadward kyng gret Aylmer bisscop & Aelfger erl and Toly and alle mine þeynes on Suffolke and Norfolke frendlike.

And ic kithe ou þat ic wille þat þat lond at Cunegestone lige into Seynt Eadmundes minstre and alle þe þinge þat þer to mid rithte bireð mid sake and mid sokne so ful and so forth so ihe alle for Gode witen þat it mid rithte in bureð.
